# Beryozovsky, Republic of Bashkortostan

}}
Beryozovsky () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Ishtuganovsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 4 as of 2010. There is 1 street.
Geography
Beryozovsky is located 51 km east of Meleuz (the district's administrative centre) by road. Syrtlanovo is the nearest rural locality.
